## Enhancement
We should add support for caching plans with hints in the prepared and non-prepared plan caches.

## Example
The select query in the following example does not currently get cached.

```
set @@session.tidb_enable_non_prepared_plan_cache = 1;
SELECT  /*+ max_execution_time(2000) */  * FROM foo WHERE a = a + 1;
SELECT  /*+ max_execution_time(2000) */  * FROM foo WHERE a = a + 1;
select @@session.last_plan_from_cache;
```

